text: Jean Van Guysse was a Belgian gymnast. He competed in the men's artistic individual all-around event at the 1908 Summer Olympics and won a silver medal in the team event at the 1920 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing Category:Year of death missing Category:Belgian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Belgium Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic silver medalists for Belgium Category:Medalists at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic medalists in gymnastics Category:Place of birth missing
